      "layout": "The site employs a max-width layout (approximately 900px, derived from inner content blocks) for primary content, which is then centered. The hero section is full-bleed, often featuring a large graphic or logo against a contrasting background. Throughout the page, content is arranged in clear, distinct blocks, often in two-column layouts where text and imagery (or another content block) sit side-by-side. Vertical spacing between sections is generous and consistent, creating a breathable yet structured feel. Navigation is minimalist, typically featuring discrete text links that integrate visually with the blocky design.",
      "imagery": "Imagery follows a stark, functional treatment. Product images appear against solid accent colored backgrounds or are tightly cropped within a blocky system. Photography, when present (e.g., people), is embedded directly into the layout without frames or overlays, adopting the inherent rectangularity of the content block. Iconography is absent, favoring a text-and-block dominant approach. Overall, imagery plays a supportive, content-rich role rather than a decorative one, fitting seamlessly into the rigid grid.",
